# Copy to .env.local and fill in the value. NEVER commit .env.local.
# The ONLY secret this app needs: an Anthropic API key for the turn-1 / turn-2 model calls.
# (The pre-LLM refusal demo runs with NO key — it never reaches the model.)
#
# Gotcha: an EMPTY or conflicting ambient ANTHROPIC_API_KEY in your shell SHADOWS
# .env.local (Next.js will not override an existing process.env key). Ensure no empty
# ambient key is set. Save .env.local as UTF-8 WITHOUT a BOM. See README §4.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
